
& pain_resistance
 
 >> Help: Pain Resistance (Advantage)
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Add +1 BTH to Conscious Roll.
 Receive only 1 damage from ammo explosions.
 
 Result: You take less damage from ammo explosions, but you are more likely to
 go unconscious.
 
 For a detailed look at this advantage, see our online documentation:
 docs.btmux.com/index.php/Skills%2C_Stats%2C_Attributes%2C_and_Advantages
 
